 degrees of freedom is 2. The integrability conditions of\nLagrange multipliers n_0, l_0, and e^A_0 are Ricci identities. The equations of\nmotion of the canonical variables have also been shown.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 28 Apr 2018 05:36:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 24 Jul 2018 11:02:18 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 8 Oct 2018 17:45:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-09"}
